originalText.text: As a gift for my Fiancé I paid for the master class. The live class was supposed to take place November 2023. We are now in January of 2024 and the class continues to be pushed out with what seems to be no guarantee of ever actually occurring. As a result we asked for a refund. I have yet to receive a response from our representative Matt. Given that the live portion of the program is what brought us to Sang Lucci we were willing to pay the $4000. We are not willing to pay for pre-recorded videos especially not that amount of money. To collect money and then not deliver the product is misleading and poor business. I highly  recommend that people looking to learn, go to another source as this company will dodge you and not deliver what you paid for.
